main: ^It is an establishment that showcases a ‘state of the art’ crocodile farming system in the Davao City, Philippines. They educate people about the natural world of the crocodiles and their connections with nature, not only the crocodile but also the wild animals inside the park.

c-0: ^It is a zoo which housed different animals such as crocodiles, birds, snakes, monkeys among many others and the most advanced crocodile park in the Philippines.
